|-------|-------|-------|------|-----------------|
| Qwen3.5-0.8B (Q8) | 0/13 | 136 | 647s | — |
| Qwen3.5-2B (Q8) | 11/13 | 45 | 419s | all passed tasks correct |
| Qwen3.5-4B (Q8) | 13/13 | 35 | 582s | **all 13 correct** |
| Qwen3.5-9B (Q8) | 13/13 | 30 | 651s | 12/13 correct (T01 hallucinated) |
| Claude Opus 4.6 | varies | varies | 30–120s/call | ✓ |

**Per-call latency (CPU-only, tuned igllama):**

- 0.8B Q8: 2–10s/call
- 2B Q8: 3–15s/call
- 4B Q8: 10–65s/call
- 9B Q8: 15–85s/call

